# Baked Gaia world scenes — regenerable via BuildXxxMedium and exceed
# GitHub's 100 MB per-file hard limit after the PWSky retrofit step
# (PW Sky.prefab + Lighting + weather + post-process + skybox material clone
# add ~70 MB to each scene). Source of truth for runtime is the bake
# artifacts in C:/Dev/.shared/baked/planet/layer_0/ + the deployed server
# binary, NOT this Unity authoring scene. Re-bake any time:
#   GaiaHeadlessPipeline.BuildConiferousMedium / BuildAlpineMedium / etc.
Assets/Scenes/GaiaWorld_*.unity
Assets/Scenes/GaiaWorld_*.unity.meta
